message.body: Hey Ray, happy new year! I hear you're in town. I'm playin in beehoven's 9th symphony tomorrow afternoon in colchester if youre interested
Hey Gabe - happy New Years to you too!! What time are you playing tomorrow? My folks are here and I'm gonna have to coordinate with them
3 pm at Elley Long music center
Me and Bryan' ll be there !
Cool, ill have some tickets at will call for yal
Hey Gabe - we had to bounce early, great job tho ..I had no idea that you played in a symphony orchestra
And thanks for hooking us up with tickets
